### Refresh Tokens
POST {{BASE}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{REFRESH}}"
}

### Logout
POST {{BASE}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{REFRESH}}"
}

### Change Password
